{"tid":1403872,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[技術分析]港鐵可載客量及有效封鎖路線之部署","createTime":"2019-08-04T00:15:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T12:52:30.000Z","uid":98860,"like":111,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"484b4773be4fb4bafdf2da9d73989624776882ac","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:15:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>總結人手計算</ins></strong><br />\n以佔領7成車廂為前題,<br />\n荃灣觀塘線:<br />\n每分鐘要429人準備上車,每班車要1715人<br />\n東鐵線:<br />\n每分鐘要525人準備上車,每班車要2625人<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>封鎖路線安排(請看圖示</ins>)</strong><br />\nA) S1-E1係Tier 1路線, 首先考慮。<br />\n安排考慮前題係車程都係大概15分鐘,讓弟兄有時間番去S1, 做到每半個鐘loop一次。夠人手可以安排埋S2-E2, S3-E3。<br />\nB) 封鎖轉乘點最大限度影響MTR。<br />\nC)封鎖最多人上班既站。<br />\n<br />\n注意:<br />\n計算未考慮第一次上車幾多%弟兄會上到車。<br />\n計算未考慮弟兄中途流失率。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>佔領車廂所需人手計算</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AbKXNg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AbKXNg.jpg&h=67989cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>路線封鎖部署</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npaDhCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnpaDhCY.jpg&h=122ccb54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef.:<br />\n<br />\nPanel on Transport Subcommittee on Matters Relating to Railways Meeting on 19 April 2016 - &quot;Updated background brief on capacity and loading of MTR trains &quot;   LC Paper No. CB(4)854/15-16(08) <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr15-16/english/panels/tp/tp_rdp/papers/tp_rdp20160419cb4-854-8-e.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr15-16%2Fenglish%2Fpanels%2Ftp%2Ftp_rdp%2Fpapers%2Ftp_rdp20160419cb4-854-8-e.pdf&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=81903bd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr15-16/english/panels/tp/tp_rdp/papers/tp_rdp20160419cb4-854-8-e.pdf</a>  <br />\n<br />\nMTR HISTORIC PATRONAGE FIGURES  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/investor/patronage.php#search\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fen%2Fcorporate%2Finvestor%2Fpatronage.php%23search&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=4b1ee7a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/investor/patronage.php#search</a>  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/operations/detail_worldclass.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fen%2Fcorporate%2Foperations%2Fdetail_worldclass.html&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=689854d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/operations/detail_worldclass.html</a>  <br />\n<br />\nLegislative Council Panel on Transport Subcommittee on Matters Relating to Railways -&quot;Capacity and Loading of MTR Trains&quot;  CB(1)980/13-14(03) <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr13-14/english/panels/tp/tp_rdp/papers/tp_rdp0228cb1-980-3-e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr13-14%2Fenglish%2Fpanels%2Ftp%2Ftp_rdp%2Fpapers%2Ftp_rdp0228cb1-980-3-e&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=8f0af004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr13-14/english/panels/tp/tp_rdp/papers/tp_rdp0228cb1-980-3-e</a><br />\n<br />\n大家為左番到工, 喺地鐵唔好企太密, 要1平方米少過4個人(&lt;4ppsm)。 你知啦太迫個人都唔舒服。 仲有人手唔夠可以試下用小物件等佢關唔到就唔好用背包咁傻仔。最好細細件好難睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為盡責既打工奴我當然都會盡力搭地鐵番工, 但係搭黎搭去都搭唔到咁我都無計呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山, 各自發功。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f5c4e9bbea8149fb2190b7a14b1deff8175e2a8","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:16:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9e4f8ed5dd2854404c54341cd55a0e7098d78d3a","tid":1403872,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:16:45.000Z","msg":"帶大型物品有冇幫助？"},{"pid":"a53af6ea1e0844b67b089f73aa82b62c4caec225","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"9e4f8ed5dd2854404c54341cd55a0e7098d78d3a","tid":1403872,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:16:45.000Z","msg":"帶大型物品有冇幫助？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:17:45.000Z","msg":"有但個個帶會俾狗拉,同埋易比人分到邊啲係所謂&quot;搞事&quot;。"},{"pid":"f90fa32684614b96fd5e97652467e3fbf5dbd52f","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:18:33.000Z","msg":"幫我罷工呀弟兄,星期一唔想番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6788ac00fd0b40336ef0dcc562f2d2641b076fdd","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:22:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26d4f233bb116e7cf2c5300f65d541ce4c2d62e8","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:28:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f81669fd30e5abbe1a82887e48160dee8f56e678","tid":1403872,"uid":283166,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"a53af6ea1e0844b67b089f73aa82b62c4caec225","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"9e4f8ed5dd2854404c54341cd55a0e7098d78d3a","tid":1403872,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:16:45.000Z","msg":"帶大型物品有冇幫助？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:17:45.000Z","msg":"有但個個帶會俾狗拉,同埋易比人分到邊啲係所謂&quot;搞事&quot;。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:34:34.000Z","msg":"總站上車, 拖住個篋坐底, <br />\n已經佔左一個坐位同一個企位啦,<br />\n去旅行鳩嗚唔算搞事"},{"pid":"e8aec3dfd70728bd962b617fff18eb9828dcbafc","tid":1403872,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:35:13.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"4ca8c0e15850aee1f99863869fb3247acceb9964","tid":1403872,"uid":281948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:37:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b6207765c7674e6e37b720dee9c93ae55289c404","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"quote":{"pid":"f81669fd30e5abbe1a82887e48160dee8f56e678","tid":1403872,"uid":283166,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"quote":{"pid":"a53af6ea1e0844b67b089f73aa82b62c4caec225","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":21,"dislike":0,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"9e4f8ed5dd2854404c54341cd55a0e7098d78d3a","tid":1403872,"uid":201604,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:16:45.000Z","msg":"帶大型物品有冇幫助？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:17:45.000Z","msg":"有但個個帶會俾狗拉,同埋易比人分到邊啲係所謂&quot;搞事&quot;。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:34:34.000Z","msg":"總站上車, 拖住個篋坐底, <br />\n已經佔左一個坐位同一個企位啦,<br />\n去旅行鳩嗚唔算搞事"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:38:36.000Z","msg":"總站上車其實唔係最有效, 因為車流量高, 總站坐到總站時間長要好撚多人先掂, 相反, 幾個主站來回就易好多"},{"pid":"90d6d9d2c1a791e1f92220ef01993fe03f64ee94","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:42:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00198091cb7e6df157b66fed2ffac6cf45ece0af","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:45:50.000Z","msg":"唔做好部署根本唔會知道荃灣線一小時可載量有75000人呀。"},{"pid":"19b2ce587b22c48dcaecb532bbcf04b73bd6a7de","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:58:01.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"3e090dec754d9ac51657a1714e4635a07b4e1cc1","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:10:03.000Z","msg":"[技術分析]港鐵可載客量及有效封鎖路線之部署<br />\n<a hr