本"},{"pid":"c5ddffeb79658077e45d8d0e92cad9b4edc51a16","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:14:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ff0ac02b18fa8778bcb7eedd4dd5986d84938eff","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"2f0c20ce67c6c1286537ef33c13a6db00fa255bf","tid":1403872,"uid":170294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T01:53:57.000Z","msg":"一人一個30吋喼都夠死<br />\n不過依d 都係成本"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:14:54.000Z","msg":"各自爬山"},{"pid":"13627890abb6f2396b1fed132a6800ea89912807","tid":1403872,"uid":46737,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:22:54.000Z","msg":"人地90秒出一班車,每班車要2千人即係塞5個站就要6千人, 來回東西南北兩線要18000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加上紅綠藍線隨時要搵幾十萬人先有得穩陣玩"},{"pid":"580d234147d1ea81c4bbd0c5b16e5359bada1b64","tid":1403872,"uid":213710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"484b4773be4fb4bafdf2da9d73989624776882ac","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:15:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>總結人手計算</ins></strong><br />\n以佔領7成車廂為前題,<br />\n荃灣觀塘線:<br />\n每分鐘要429人準備上車,每班車要1715人<br />\n東鐵線:<br />\n每分鐘要525人準備上車,每班車要2625人<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>封鎖路線安排(請看圖示</ins>)</strong><br />\nA) S1-E1係Tier 1路線, 首先考慮。<br />\n安排考慮前題係車程都係大概15分鐘,讓弟兄有時間番去S1, 做到每半個鐘loop一次。夠人手可以安排埋S2-E2, S3-E3。<br />\nB) 封鎖轉乘點最大限度影響MTR。<br />\nC)封鎖最多人上班既站。<br />\n<br />\n注意:<br />\n計算未考慮第一次上車幾多%弟兄會上到車。<br />\n計算未考慮弟兄中途流失率。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>佔領車廂所需人手計算</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AbKXNg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AbKXNg.jpg&h=67989cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>路線封鎖部署</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npaDhCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnpaDhCY.jpg&h=122ccb54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef.:<br />\n<br />\nPanel on Transport Subcommittee on Matters Relating to Railways Meeting on 19 April 2016 - &quot;Updated background brief on capacity and loading of MTR trains &quot;   LC Paper No. CB(4)854/15-16(08) <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr15-16/english/panels/tp/tp_rdp/papers/tp_rdp20160419cb4-854-8-e.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr15-16%2Fenglish%2Fpanels%2Ftp%2Ftp_rdp%2Fpapers%2Ftp_rdp20160419cb4-854-8-e.pdf&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=81903bd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr15-16/english/panels/tp/tp_rdp/papers/tp_rdp20160419cb4-854-8-e.pdf</a>  <br />\n<br />\nMTR HISTORIC PATRONAGE FIGURES  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/investor/patronage.php#search\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fen%2Fcorporate%2Finvestor%2Fpatronage.php%23search&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=4b1ee7a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/investor/patronage.php#search</a>  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/operations/detail_worldclass.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fen%2Fcorporate%2Foperations%2Fdetail_worldclass.html&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=689854d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/operations/detail_worldclass.html</a>  <br />\n<br />\nLegislative Council Panel on Transport Subcommittee on Matters Relating to Railways -&quot;Capacity and Loading of MTR Trains&quot;  CB(1)980/13-14(03) <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr13-14/english/panels/tp/tp_rdp/papers/tp_rdp0228cb1-980-3-e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr13-14%2Fenglish%2Fpanels%2Ftp%2Ftp_rdp%2Fpapers%2Ftp_rdp0228cb1-980-3-e&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=8f0af004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr13-14/english/panels/tp/tp_rdp/papers/tp_rdp0228cb1-980-3-e</a><br />\n<br />\n大家為左番到工, 喺地鐵唔好企太密, 要1平方米少過4個人(&lt;4ppsm)。 你知啦太迫個人都唔舒服。 仲有人手唔夠可以試下用小物件等佢關唔到就唔好用背包咁傻仔。最好細細件好難睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為盡責既打工奴我當然都會盡力搭地鐵番工, 但係搭黎搭去都搭唔到咁我都無計呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山, 各自發功。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:23:49.000Z","msg":"攞十字匙Lock幕門 簡單快捷方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2efd094c7a119246e013fc1a9ba504e4fa1e923a","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"580d234147d1ea81c4bbd0c5b16e5359bada1b64","tid":1403872,"uid":213710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"484b4773be4fb4bafdf2da9d73989624776882ac","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:15:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>總結人手計算</ins></strong><br />\n以佔領7成車廂為前題,<br />\n荃灣觀塘線:<br />\n每分鐘要429人準備上車,每班車要1715人<br />\n東鐵線:<br />\n每分鐘要525人準備上車,每班車要2625人<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>封鎖路線安排(請看圖示</ins>)</strong><br />\nA) S1-E1係Tier 1路線, 首先考慮。<br />\n安排考慮前題係車程都係大概15分鐘,讓弟兄有時間番去S1, 做到每半個鐘loop一次。夠人手可以安排埋S2-E2, S3-E3。<br />\nB) 封鎖轉乘點最大限度影響MTR。<br />\nC)封鎖最多人上班既站。<br />\n<br />\n注意:<br />\n計算未考慮第一次上車幾多%弟兄會上到車。<br />\n計算未考慮弟兄中途流失率。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>佔領車廂所需人手計算</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AbKXNg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AbKXNg.jpg&h=67989cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>路線封鎖部署</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npaDhCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnpaDhCY.jpg&h=122ccb54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef.:<br />\n<br />\nPanel on Transport Subcommittee on Matters Relating to Railways Meeting on 19 April 2016 - &quot;Updated background brief on capacity and loading of MTR trains &quot;   LC Paper No. CB(4)854/15-16(08) <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr15-16/english/panels/tp/tp_rdp/papers/tp_rdp20160419cb4-854-8-e.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr15-16%2Fenglish%2Fpanels%2Ftp%2Ftp_rdp%2Fpapers%2Ftp_rdp20160419cb4-854-8-e.pdf&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=81903bd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr15-16/english/panels/tp/tp_rdp/papers/tp_rdp20160419cb4-854-8-e.pdf</a>  <br />\n<br />\nMTR HISTORIC PATRONAGE FIGURES  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/investor/patronage.php#search\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fen%2Fcorporate%2Finvestor%2Fpatronage.php%23search&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=4b1ee7a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/investor/patronage.php#search</a>  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/operations/detail_worldclass.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fen%2Fcorporate%2Foperations%2Fdetail_worldclass.html&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=689854d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/operations/detail_worldclass.html</a>  <br />\n<br />\nLegislative Council Panel on Transport Subcommittee on Matters Relating to Railways -&quot;Capacity and Loading of MTR Trains&quot;  CB(1)980/13-14(03) <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr13-14/english/panels/tp/tp_rdp/papers/tp_rdp0228cb1-980-3-e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr13-14%2Fenglish%2Fpanels%2Ftp%2Ftp_rdp%2Fpapers%2Ftp_rdp0228cb1-980-3-e&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=8f0af004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr13-14/english/panels/tp/tp_rdp/papers/tp_rdp0228cb1-980-3-e</a><br />\n<br />\n大家為左番到工, 喺地鐵唔好企太密, 要1平方米少過4個人(&lt;4ppsm)。 你知啦太迫個人都唔舒服。 仲有人手唔夠可以試下用小物件等佢關唔到就唔好用背包咁傻仔。最好細細件好難睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為盡責既打工奴我當然都會盡力搭地鐵番工, 但係搭黎搭去都搭唔到咁我都無計呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山, 各自發功。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:23:49.000Z","msg":"攞十字匙Lock幕門 簡單快捷方便<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:25:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />無諗過"},{"pid":"3ea818a502b803fba806f14ba421d9568298075c","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:27:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee450d18d61fa5f466d65b3a39637b4327e102d5","tid":1403872,"uid":213710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2efd094c7a119246e013fc1a9ba504e4fa1e923a","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"580d234147d1ea81c4bbd0c5b16e5359bada1b64","tid":1403872,"uid":213710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"484b4773be4fb4bafdf2da9d73989624776882ac","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:15:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>總結人手計算</ins></strong><br />\n以佔領7成車廂為前題,<br />\n荃灣觀塘線:<br />\n每分鐘要429人準備上車,每班車要1715人<br />\n東鐵線:<br />\n每分鐘要525人準備上車,每班車要2625人<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>封鎖路線安排(請看圖示</ins>)</strong><br />\nA) S1-E1係Tier 1路線, 首先考慮。<br />\n安排考慮前題係車程都係大概15分鐘,讓弟兄有時間番去S1, 做到每半個鐘loop一次。夠人手可以安排埋S2-E2, S3-E3。<br />\nB) 封鎖轉乘點最大限度影響MTR。<br />\nC)封鎖最多人上班既站。<br />\n<br />\n注意:<br />\n計算未考慮第一次上車幾多%弟兄會上到車。<br />\n計算未考慮弟兄中途流失率。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>佔領車廂所需人手計算</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AbKXNg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AbKXNg.jpg&h=67989cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>路線封鎖部署</ins><br />