T00:16:45.000Z","msg":"帶大型物品有冇幫助？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:17:45.000Z","msg":"有但個個帶會俾狗拉,同埋易比人分到邊啲係所謂&quot;搞事&quot;。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T02:48:18.000Z","msg":"放低左鬼知邊個既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:07:33.000Z","msg":"平時日日成個九龍塘都拉喼客<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">你地千萬唔好帶大喼 會阻到人架 不過趕飛機 趕時間 無法啦</span></strong>"},{"pid":"a129b498d00d55af6bd4f676a9148d1e9db865cd","tid":1403872,"uid":170294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:09:55.000Z","msg":"MTR九龍東 如果有事 會由九龍灣車廠出空車 <br />\n為保太子至九龍塘 放棄油塘果邊<br />\n<br />\n所以你懂的"},{"pid":"f2b80b3574bfeaf5cdfceaf5a24183a3d2910391","tid":1403872,"uid":28244,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:16:56.000Z","msg":"up另外有冇車既技術討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />聽日唔返工但又好迷茫應該點"},{"pid":"490b4c4677613ff8939ed8cfc58eb00e85104b29","tid":1403872,"uid":103821,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"484b4773be4fb4bafdf2da9d73989624776882ac","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T00:15:58.000Z","msg":"<strong><ins>總結人手計算</ins></strong><br />\n以佔領7成車廂為前題,<br />\n荃灣觀塘線:<br />\n每分鐘要429人準備上車,每班車要1715人<br />\n東鐵線:<br />\n每分鐘要525人準備上車,每班車要2625人<br />\n<br />\n<strong><ins>封鎖路線安排(請看圖示</ins>)</strong><br />\nA) S1-E1係Tier 1路線, 首先考慮。<br />\n安排考慮前題係車程都係大概15分鐘,讓弟兄有時間番去S1, 做到每半個鐘loop一次。夠人手可以安排埋S2-E2, S3-E3。<br />\nB) 封鎖轉乘點最大限度影響MTR。<br />\nC)封鎖最多人上班既站。<br />\n<br />\n注意:<br />\n計算未考慮第一次上車幾多%弟兄會上到車。<br />\n計算未考慮弟兄中途流失率。<br />\n<br />\n<ins>佔領車廂所需人手計算</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9AbKXNg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9AbKXNg.jpg&h=67989cb5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<ins>路線封鎖部署</ins><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/npaDhCY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnpaDhCY.jpg&h=122ccb54&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef.:<br />\n<br />\nPanel on Transport Subcommittee on Matters Relating to Railways Meeting on 19 April 2016 - &quot;Updated background brief on capacity and loading of MTR trains &quot;   LC Paper No. CB(4)854/15-16(08) <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr15-16/english/panels/tp/tp_rdp/papers/tp_rdp20160419cb4-854-8-e.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr15-16%2Fenglish%2Fpanels%2Ftp%2Ftp_rdp%2Fpapers%2Ftp_rdp20160419cb4-854-8-e.pdf&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=81903bd4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr15-16/english/panels/tp/tp_rdp/papers/tp_rdp20160419cb4-854-8-e.pdf</a>  <br />\n<br />\nMTR HISTORIC PATRONAGE FIGURES  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/investor/patronage.php#search\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fen%2Fcorporate%2Finvestor%2Fpatronage.php%23search&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=4b1ee7a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/investor/patronage.php#search</a>  <br />\n<a href=\"https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/operations/detail_worldclass.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mtr.com.hk%2Fen%2Fcorporate%2Foperations%2Fdetail_worldclass.html&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=689854d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.mtr.com.hk/en/corporate/operations/detail_worldclass.html</a>  <br />\n<br />\nLegislative Council Panel on Transport Subcommittee on Matters Relating to Railways -&quot;Capacity and Loading of MTR Trains&quot;  CB(1)980/13-14(03) <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr13-14/english/panels/tp/tp_rdp/papers/tp_rdp0228cb1-980-3-e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.legco.gov.hk%2Fyr13-14%2Fenglish%2Fpanels%2Ftp%2Ftp_rdp%2Fpapers%2Ftp_rdp0228cb1-980-3-e&d=DPPAsuUI5qXcFl7kT6ByvGjFlCc76q8eB7f9T8a%2Fn1E%3D&h=8f0af004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.legco.gov.hk/yr13-14/english/panels/tp/tp_rdp/papers/tp_rdp0228cb1-980-3-e</a><br />\n<br />\n大家為左番到工, 喺地鐵唔好企太密, 要1平方米少過4個人(&lt;4ppsm)。 你知啦太迫個人都唔舒服。 仲有人手唔夠可以試下用小物件等佢關唔到就唔好用背包咁傻仔。最好細細件好難睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n作為盡責既打工奴我當然都會盡力搭地鐵番工, 但係搭黎搭去都搭唔到咁我都無計呀。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">兄弟爬山, 各自發功。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:19:13.000Z","msg":"手足們可以一人一gip, 又佔空間又可以當「國師盾」用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ef7cfe79b01b89bdf56c98040475f1186f98c27","tid":1403872,"uid":263778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:20:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n8月5日幫人罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12df8138be7af2a738eac3a0fe9807970616f4a8","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:36:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b27594985cee11279e542b3b5d6834cd09d7e0a3","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8ef7cfe79b01b89bdf56c98040475f1186f98c27","tid":1403872,"uid":263778,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:20:04.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n8月5日幫人罷工<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T03:43:37.000Z","msg":"多謝,我都會幫自己"},{"pid":"66c9c7e34a8f360bee56fbc4c8f876b68cfae6d4","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:08:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41ee31c22249ea1b7a8d9ff4849096fe6b1fda22","tid":1403872,"uid":238275,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"621f463561cf673669340621858cdc7645b7c1cf","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:43:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加油"},{"pid":"d29e30bdce822e246b7531de368845dc479be924","tid":1403872,"uid":57304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:50:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f029785f7ca5056f00caa4add6aaee0bb8f91547","tid":1403872,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T04:51:38.000Z","msg":"觀察到新戰術：四散游擊，街坊落場<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1402338\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1402338</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fda3a6830fc0451e46d2debab0a25f69ff1529f0","tid":1403872,"uid":98860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:18:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab1096d9dc909a686ef1843f9e1ad9629a4689d1","tid":1403872,"uid":237143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:29:35.000Z","msg":"千祈唔好擺幾個煙餅落月台垃圾桶  一陣要疏散人群<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c190e2c1f316b3383833b80a8dd353783e44fd","tid":1403872,"uid":204031,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:50:03.000Z","msg":"尋晚發夢，想搭地鐵<br />\n見到全部<span style=\"color: red;\">入閘機貼哂RFID貼，無人用到八達通入閘</span><br />\n然後個夢唔知點解閃一閃我終於入咗閘<br />\n入面好多人都拖個<span style=\"color: red;\">24吋或以上大喼，揹個大背囊</span><br />\n月台車箱都係咁，我問一問隔離個大波妹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n：你地裝住啲咩，同埋要去邊？<br />\n點知佢個喼係空架！背囊係空水樽、足球、排球、毛巾之類好輕嘅嘢<br />\n仲有件羽絨褸！我問佢：天氣咁熱做咩拎羽絨褸，你傻架？<br />\n佢答我：你就傻，搭地鐵涼冷氣不知幾舒服，我<span style=\"color: red;\">來來回回呢２個站搭咗廿次</span>啦<br />\n然後我就醒咗啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c26d4a7fc0c9166f47a36d854a567ae5c6d3a2b","tid":1403872,"uid":170294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:56:51.000Z","msg":"明天拖30吋喼去搭車返工 係和理非 最接受的<br />\n你知啦 返工要拎好多野 背囊仔邊夠拎"},{"pid":"3d2116f3e62350a05d57499b317ae7692e8d90ef","tid":1403872,"uid":56206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T06:03:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}